# Package scope (Galipette monorepo)

Follow these boundaries when adding or moving code. Keep each concern in its designated area.

| Concern | Location | Put here |
|--------|-----------|----------|
| **Runtime UI, routes, client/server app behavior** | `apps/web` | Pages, components, hooks, app-specific API routes, runtime config consumed by the web app. |
| **Build-time schemas & shared types** | `packages/content-schema` | Zod (or similar) schemas, TypeScript types/interfaces for entities and content that **both** builder and consumers rely on. No markdown parsing, no I/O to disk beyond what that package needs for schema utilities. |
| **Markdown → mdast & wiki syntax** | `packages/content-parser` | Remark/unified pipeline, Obsidian wikilink parsing into mdast (`wikiLink` nodes), operand/display helpers, resolving wiki nodes against the entity corpus (depends on `content-schema`). No vault scanning or artifact writes. |
| **Compile-step orchestration over parsed markdown** | `packages/content-resolver` | Merges front-matter operands with body AST operands, attaches `compiledContent` and merged `references` (`refSources`). Consumed by `content-builder`; depends on `content-parser` + `content-schema`. |
| **Markdown compiler & content build pipeline** | `packages/content-builder` | Vault scan, front matter + validation orchestration, slug generation, invokes `content-resolver`, writes outputs, CLI/build scripts. Depends on `content-schema`, `content-parser`, `content-resolver`; does **not** define long-lived runtime APIs over compiled data. |
| **Local API over compiled artifacts** | `packages/compiled-content` | Reading bundled JSON (or generated data), resolving slugs/references, navigation trees, graph helpers — the **stable library** the web app imports at runtime after a build. Generated files under this package are **outputs** of `content-builder`, not hand-edited source of truth. |

## Quick checks

- **New React page or route?** → `apps/web`.
- **New/changed entity shape or validation rules shared by build + app?** → `packages/content-schema`.
- **New Remark plugin, mdast shape, or wikilink parsing helper?** → `packages/content-parser`.
- **New merge/resolve step after validation but before graph/write?** → `packages/content-resolver` (or extend it).
- **New transform from `.md` to structured data or vault scan / CLI?** → `packages/content-builder`.
- **New query/helper over built `entities.json` / graph / slug index?** → `packages/compiled-content`.

Avoid duplicating schema definitions outside `content-schema`. Avoid embedding markdown compilation inside `apps/web` or `compiled-content`.
